03:28.379 --> 03:30.740
Oh, he doesn't know what he's missing.

03:32.460 --> 03:35.459
I bet Lee wouldn't be
talking to Emma Bunton.

03:35.460 --> 03:37.179
Damn right we wouldn't be talking.

03:37.180 --> 03:40.819
