03:53.780 --> 03:55.699
Oh! Who did you pick?

03:55.699 --> 03:56.739
You first.

03:56.740 --> 03:58.938
Well, obviously me
first, but who after me?

03:58.939 --> 04:00.618
Come on. Who? I won't be offended.

04:00.620 --> 04:01.938
It's just a game.

04:01.939 --> 04:06.539
Um... Well, I suppose if I have
to say, then I would pick...

04:07.860 --> 04:10.699
...Michael Lorenzo.

04:10.699 --> 04:11.818
Who?

04:11.819 --> 04:14.099
Oh, you won't know him. He's my dentist.

04:18.459 --> 04:20.019
Can't choose your dentist.

04:20.019 --> 04:21.059
Why not?

04:21.060 --> 04:22.619
It's supposed to be a celebrity.

04:22.620 --> 04:24.060
Oh.

04:25.220 --> 04:26.939
Mine would be Hugh Jackman.

04:26.939 --> 04:28.899
You just said Tom Hardy!

04:28.899 --> 04:30.499
And now I'm saying Hugh Jackman.

04:30.500 --> 04:32.779
It doesn't mean Tom Hardy has to get out.

04:34.139 --> 04:35.939
