04:35.939 --> 04:37.579
Emma Bunton.

04:37.579 --> 04:40.298
Oh, good choice. She's a very
attractive woman.

04:40.300 --> 04:42.978
Oh, yeah, it's easy to be unbothered
when it's someone famous.

04:42.980 --> 04:45.137
