07:48.108 --> 07:49.987
Hang on. Your wife.

07:49.987 --> 07:51.226
She's not Lucy, is she?

07:51.228 --> 07:52.387
Yeah.

07:52.387 --> 07:56.947
I thought I recognised your surname.
Yeah, Lucy. Lovely girl.

07:56.947 --> 07:59.387
