14:12.113 --> 14:14.792
She is mingling, with me,
a potential donor.

14:14.793 --> 14:18.033
I'm the minglee, she's the minger...
mingler.

14:20.113 --> 14:21.631
Come on.

14:21.633 --> 14:23.871
You go. I'll be over in a second.

14:23.873 --> 14:26.432
I just want to get a selfie
with Emma, if that's all right.

14:26.432 --> 14:28.152
Always happy to help the donors.

14:28.153 --> 14:30.991
